    <div type="edition" xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:83215">
        <ab xml:lang="san-Latn" rendition="class:grantha maturity:83215">
            <lb n="1"/><unclear>svasti śrī</unclear>
        </ab>
        
            <p>
		tiripuvaṉa-c-cakkara-vattikaḷ <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi> cuntara-pāṇṭiya-tēvaṟku yāṇṭu 10 Āvatu kēyya-māṇikka-vaḷaṉāṭṭu vaṭakāl
		<lb n="2"/>parivaṭṭa nakaram pukalōkattu Uṭaiyār pañcavaṉ mātēvicuvaram uṭaiyār kōyilukku tiruvātavū<supplied reason="omitted">r</supplied>-nāyaṉārai Ēṟi aruḷa paṇṇiṉa ṉākaiyāṉa
		<lb n="3"/>cōḻa ku<supplied reason="omitted">lava</supplied>lli paṭṭiṉattu tiruppaḷḷi-p-pāṟṟu ṉāyakattāril Āṇṭāṉ kōtayāṉa kulōttuṅka rāyaṉēṉ Iṉ-ṉāyaṉāṟkku Amutupaṭikkum t<choice><sic>a</sic><corr>i</corr></choice>ruviḷakku
		<lb n="4" break="no"/>m nāyanāṟ<choice><sic>t</sic><corr>k</corr></choice>ku koṇṭa<unclear>ṭa</unclear>kantaṉ uṭaiyān nilamum nattamum Āvatu Ivūr piṭākai cankuṇaveḷi paṇappāṟṟukku vaṭakku taṭi mūṉṟu viṭṭuma
		<lb n="5" break="no"/>ṟkku Amutupaṭikkum tiruvi
		<lb n="6"/>Ōṭai Eṉṟu pēr kūvappaṭṭa nilam mā mummāvaraiyum kaṇapati vāykkālukku mēṟkku puṟaṅkarampa-ṉāṭṭu vēḷāṉ maṉaikku valivala-nāṭu vēḷāṉ maṉai Iru
		<lb n="7" break="no"/>ppukkum 1/10 <g ref="sym:tam-nilam"/>m I-nilamā mummāvaraiyum Iṉ-nāyanāṟku Amutupaṭikkum tiruviḷakkum cant<supplied reason="omitted">i</supplied>rātityavarai cella-k kaṭavat' āka-k koṇṭu Iṭṭēṉ Āṇṭāṉ kō
		<lb n="8"/>taiyāṉa kulōttuṅka-rāyaṉ ēṉ Ik-kōyil Akrāṇam tiruvārūr ammāṉ eḻuttu - Ik-kōyil tēvakammi piramīcuvara paṭṭaṉ Eḻuttu
		<lb n="9"/>Ik-kōyil kaṇakkaṉ paṉaṅk' uṭaiyāṉ vītiviṭaṅka-p perumāṉ Eḻu<supplied reason="omitted">ttu</supplied>
	</p>
        
	
